Wandering Keg;;10;Jump inside the barrel, gain a 520 point Shield and roll towards the cursor, dealing 30 damage to enemies in the way and knocking them back. Lasts for 5 seconds, or until the Shield is broken.
Storm, Earth, Fire;;10;Split into three elemental spirits for 15.15 seconds, each with 50% of your maximum Health, and enables two new leaping attacks for use. Storm attacks at range for 30 damage. Earth attacks slowly for 20 damage and slows enemies by 25%. Fire attacks quickly for 18 damage.
