Combustion;;16;Breath of Fire deals 60 bonus damage immediately to Brew-soaked enemies instead of lighting them on fire.
Combat Stance (Trait);;16;Shields from Fortifying Brew last for an additional 2 seconds after drinking stops.
Resurgence of the Storm;;20;Upon dying, revive back at your Altar after 5 seconds. This can occur once every 120 seconds.
Bolt of the Storm;;20;Activate to teleport to a nearby location. 40s cooldown.
